<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>org.bellz.convertall.convertall</id>

  <name>ConvertAll</name>
  <summary>A flexible unit conversion tool</summary>

  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-2.0-or-later</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      With ConvertAll, you can combine the units any way you want. If you want to convert from inches per decade, that&apos;s fine. Or from meter-pounds. Or from cubic nautical miles. The units don&apos;t have to make sense to anyone else.
    </p>
  </description>

